      <title class="- topic/title " outputclass="Heading 3">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">5307.104-90</ph> Solicitation Release</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a) For ACAT programs, see <xref href="http://static.e-publishing.af.mil/production/1/saf_aq/publication/afi63-101_20-101/afi63-101_20-101.pdf"
                  scope="external"
                  format="pdf"
                  class="- topic/xref ">
               <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">AFI 63-101/20-101</u>
            </xref> (paragraph 4.3.1) and <xref href="http://www.esd.whs.mil/Portals/54/Documents/DD/issuances/dodi/500002_dodi_2015.pdf?ver=2017-08-11-170656-430"
                  scope="external"
                  format="pdf?ver=2017-08-11-170656-430"
                  class="- topic/xref ">
               <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">DoDI 5000.02</u>
            </xref>. </p>
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(b) For all other acquisitions, the contracting officer must not release the solicitation until the approval official has approved the Acquisition Plan (AP) unless the acquisition is being conducted pursuant to the authority of FAR 6.302-2, unusual and compelling urgency.</p>
         <p id="p__Toc38364752" outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p "> (c) For acquisitions utilizing policies and procedures in accordance with FAR 15.3, see FAR 15.303 and the <xref href="http://www.acq.osd.mil/dpap/policy/policyvault/USA004370-14-DPAP.pdf"
                  scope="external"
                  format="pdf"
                  class="- topic/xref ">
               <u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">DoD Source Selection Procedures</u>
            </xref>.</p>
